logue of religions, religious education, and peace. These show how relevant the study of religions can be –when it is distinctly and responsibly defined.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aMethodology.  aNew Religion.  aStudy of Religions.  aSyncretism.  aTradition.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023854908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION  2013z978311031734308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE, RELIGIONSWISS., JUDAISTIK  2013z9783110317336oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978161451250940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451191540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614511915423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781614511915/original  a978-3-11-023854-9  DGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031734-3  E-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION  2013b2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2013  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014